22 May 2017The African National Congress will hold its 5th National Policy Conference at the Nasrec Expo Centre in Soweto, Gauteng, from the 30th of June to the 05th of July 2017. The National Policy Conference, held at least once in every five years, reviews ANC policy and makes recommendations on the amendments or new policies to the National Conference.As the closing date for media accreditation applications is drawing to a close, members of the media are urged to apply online through the ANC website. The application form will be available until the 2nd of June 2017.Late applications will not be entertained.Click on this link to apply: http://www.anc.org.za/forms/media-accreditation-application-formIssued by the African National CongressEnquiries Zizi Kodwa 082 330 4910 National SpokespersonKhusela Sangoni 082 854 5707 National Communications Manager